text: The Second Cabinet of Lars Løkke Rasmussen was the Government of Denmark, in office between 28 June 2015 and 28 November 2016, where Lars Løkke Rasmussen third cabinet took over. It was a single-party minority government consisting of Venstre, the first since Anker Jørgensen V Cabinet in 1981-82. It was supported by the Danish People's Party, the Liberal Alliance and the Conservative People's Party. ==List of ministers== {| |- | |} |} ==References== * Category:Government of Denmark Rasmussen, Lars Lokke 2 Category:2015 establishments in Denmark Category:Cabinets established in 2015 Category:2016 disestablishments in Denmark Category:Cabinets disestablished in 2016
